title: Total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in Canada 2020
summary: This graph illustrates the Total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in 2020 .
The Number of cars entering is about 1510198.09 at the start of the year .
It increases towards fall There is a peak at 2339189.19 in August .
gold: The number of cars returning to the country peaked in January and February at approximately 1.5 million before a sharp decline through March to a rate of only 400000 - 600000 for the remaining months of 2020 .
